arStrings.szText: "That is no prayer to the Light. How do you know Rathma's Prophecy?"
It was something my mother used to say. It brought our family hope before she died. Many of us are lost now, but we who remember her pray for a fresh hope.
Somber yet friendly. Hiding his true meaning.
Our house is southwest of town—you should join us for supper! We can speak more of “lambs and wolves.”
A friendly invitation. Casual but suggestive.
